column3: sentence
In which U.S. state is Area 51 located?
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Area_51 dbo:location ?uri . ?uri dbo:country res:United_States. }

column3: Which countries have places with more than two caves?
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?cave rdf:type dbo:Cave ; dbo:location ?uri . ?uri rdf:type dbo:Country } GROUP BY ?uri HAVING ( COUNT(?cave) > 2 )

column3: Give me all actors starring in movies directed by and starring William Shatner.
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?x dbo:director res:William_Shatner ; dbo:starring res:William_Shatner { ?x dbo:starring ?uri } UNION { ?x dbp:starring ?uri } }

column3: Give me the grandchildren of Bruce Lee.
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Bruce_Lee dbo:child ?child . ?child <http://dbpedia.org/property/children> ?uri }

column3: Which other weapons did the designer of the Uzi develop?
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Weapon ; dbp:designer ?x . res:Uzi dbp:designer ?x FILTER ( ?uri != res:Uzi ) }

column3: Which state of the USA has the highest population density?
column7: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:densityrank ?rank } ORDER BY ASC(?rank) LIMIT 1

column3: Which monarchs were married to a German?
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Monarch ; dbo:spouse ?spouse { ?spouse dbo:birthPlace res:Germany } UNION { ?spouse dbo:birthPlace ?p . ?p dbo:country res:Germany } }

column3: Which state of the United States of America has the highest density?
column7: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbp:densityrank ?density } ORDER BY ASC(?density) LIMIT 1

column3: Give me a list of all trumpet players that were bandleaders.
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:occupation res:Bandleader ; dbo:instrument res:Trumpet }

column3: Which U.S. states are in the same timezone as Utah?
column7: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Utah dbp:timezone ?x . ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:timezone ?x FILTER ( ?uri != res:Utah ) }

column3: Which U.S. states possess gold minerals?
column7: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates ; dbp:mineral ?mineral FILTER regex(?mineral, "gold", "i") }

column3: Who is the daughter of Ingrid Bergman married to?
column7: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Ingrid_Bergman dbo:child ?child . ?child <http://dbpedia.org/property/spouse> ?uri }

column3: Which caves have more than 3 entrances?
What are the top-10 action role-playing video games according to IGN?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Action_role-playing_video_games> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/ign> ?score } ORDER BY DESC(?score) LIMIT 10

column3: Give me all writers that won the Nobel Prize in literature.
Give me all cosmonauts.
Give me all Swiss non-profit organizations.
Which presidents were born in 1945?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/President> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?date FILTER regex(?date, "^1945") }

column3: What kind of music did Lou Reed play?
Where do the Red Sox play?
Which volcanos in Japan erupted since 2000?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Volcano> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/locatedInArea> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/eruptionYear> ?date FILTER ( year(?date) >= 2000 ) }

column3: How many films did Hal Roach produce?
What is the most frequent cause of death?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathCause> ?x . } ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri)) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

column3: Who are the four youngest MVP basketball players?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BasketballPlayer> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?date ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/highlights> ?h FILTER regex(?h, "MVP") } ORDER BY DESC(?date) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 4

Which companies have more than 1 million employees?

column3: Show me everyone who was born on Halloween.

List all the musicals with music by Leonard Bernstein.
Give me all companies in the advertising industry.
column7: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Company> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/industry> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertising> } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/industry> ?industry FILTER regex(?industry, "advertising", "i") } }

column3: Which writers studied in Istanbul?
column7: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Writer> { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/almaMater> ?x } UNION { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/education> ?x } { ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/city> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul> } UNION { ?x <http://dbpedia.org/property/city> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul> } }
